# Sales Data Analysis Project

## Overview
This project performs exploratory data analysis (EDA) on a sales dataset using Python.  
It explores trends, visualizes data, and extracts insights to support business decisions.

## Tools & Libraries
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib

## Key Steps
- Data loading and exploration
- Data cleaning
- Sales analysis by day
- Data visualization using bar charts
- Extracting insights from data

## Key Insight
- Identified the day with the highest total sales

